<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">You will have received an email from Kingsbridge confirming that <b>we have removed your account from automatic renewal</b>. <br><br>Please be advised that the email you received is generated by our system when <b>more information will be required about your job role at renewal</b>.&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><b>Your policy coverage is unaffected</b> at this time and <b>no further action is required from you at this stage</b>. However, <b>we will contact you closer to renewal to confirm your details</b>.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Kind regards,</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!User.FirstName}</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Customer Service Team</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">T: 01242 808 740</font></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>